<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wonderful-adj">wonderful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'wʌndəfl/    美 /'wʌndərfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>奇妙的；精彩的；极好的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a wonderful surprise/idea
惊喜/妙计</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The food was wonderful with reasonable prices, and we enjoyed several local dishes.
食物很棒，价格公道，我们享受了几道当地菜。</p><footer>2012 陕西</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>We are so proud of our grandmother's award. It's<strong><em>_</em></strong>(wonder).  （2019全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. wonderful  </p></div>